race.comment: DAINTREE DAZZLER (4) had been super consistent recording two placings in a row before he was rewarded with a win last time, scoring at this track over 350m (19.63). Solid formlines coming through his last run. Has hit winning form and can measure up again. BE A SHADOW (5) turned in a better effort at this track last start, finishing third behind Path To Nirvana (19.64) in a Grade 4/5. Expected to feature again. BULLSEYE BOB (6) was an impressive winner in the quickest time of the program two back then hit the frame when third at this track (17.15) last time. Must be included in calculations. BLAME ESMERALDA (8) placed last time at this track and distance - worth some thought.
